Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo. I look forward\Nto working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Domo. Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to play golf\Nwith you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we do, don't be\Ntoo hard on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to\Ncontinuing business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo... Domo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incomprehensible bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, domo, domo.\NSorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My business meeting ran a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Iwai of the Kadofuku Corporation,\NMunich branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inspector Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Domo" and a bow?\NI'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and a refill as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to meet Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's gone to\Nthe Czech Republic on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to return tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you know about Schuwald,\Nthe business tycoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come out of seclusion and\Nrestarted his business activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All the businesses under his control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and their subsidiaries have\Nrecently been reinvigorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We Japanese businessmen are\Nvery busy with Mr. Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is he laughing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Yamamoto can't help you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But he and I are just as\Nclose to Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised. I didn't think\Nhe was still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We still haven't solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I heard that\NTenma was a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were surprised.\NWas it that unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very surprised. I never would have\Nthought him capable of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually,\NI never thought he would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I went drinking with him twice\Nthree years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bad person...\NDoes that mean he's a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A good person... Or rather...\NHe didn't reveal himself freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone who doesn't\Nreveal himself a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, it just means\Nthat he wasn't too unsociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese people don't\Nusually wear these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese people are\Nhandy with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Japanese person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Japanese person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Japanese person.\NI am...Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh. ..Dad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you doing well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I called because I heard that\Nyou were in Munich.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm living here now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually Dad' my son was born.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lot has happened' but...\NI want you to see your grandson.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you come to see us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is tomorrow all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If it's after 6 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll met at...the Marian Platz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right.\NSee you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so skillful with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, lately,\Nthere have been a lot of foreigners
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who are even better at using chopsticks\Nthan Japanese people are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Doctor Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a colleague,\Nwhat kind of person was Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't that unsociable.\NWell, he was a bit indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When he held a scalpel,\Nhe was like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been called a brilliant brain surgeon,\Nand that's not an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't like to talk\Nmuch about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said that his father and\Nhis older brother were also doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he probably had no choice\Nbut to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:07:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,he said that he hasn't gone back to Japan\Nsince he became a doctor in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And his parents didn't come here\Nduring that uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They also didn't argue\Nfor their son's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that means that\Nhe has weak family ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's arrived in Munich from Prague.\NBut he has to go make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to meet us afterwards\Nat the place we're going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Would you like to come,\Ninspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be fate! We might also be\Nindebted to you in the future, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, today, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose that means that\Nhe has weak family ties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I...am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.\NPlease allow me to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Farewell Pleiades...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Farewell Pleiades!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected of you Iwai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. My song's next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A love letter from Canada!\N– A love letter from Canada!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}– What a fun trip it would be{\i0}\N– That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}– If you were with me...{\i0}\N– Woo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Tenma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}– A love letter from Canada!{\i0}\N– I am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot blend\Ninto Japanese society.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't ask for help here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no place to go home to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am... alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo, domo.\NI'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you,\NYamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Inspector Lunge,\Nthe one I told you about on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, domo. I'm Yamamoto of\NKadofuku Corporations' Munich branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your negotiations go with\NMr. Kocht in the Czech Republic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... He's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"It"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that Schuwald's right-hand man\Nasked us to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the blond boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, getting on\Nthat secretary's good side
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best way to close a deal\Nwith Mr. Schuwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I searched countless\Nused bookstores in Prague,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I finally found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. So this is the picture book!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The cover's gone and it's worn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll look good\Nif we package it nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'll have a beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,May I see that for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in Czech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. My song's next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\N– All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!\N– We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to show off\Nhis singing talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, what are you looking up\Nin that dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Czech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Czech?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have something to do\Nwith your investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No...not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're looking up\Nsomething unrelated to your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a line in a picture book.\NI liked the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know what\Nits captions said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The inspector with a picture book...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me\Nhas gotten this big."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's finally controlling that tycoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about Johan from you before.\NHe's a complete monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've done quite a few murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's become something that\NI could only wish to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I have one more thing\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Johan,\Nwhat would you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I would kill my current parents...\Nthe Lieberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because I've\Ngrown bored with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!\NMr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychoanalyst?\NWhat business do you have with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of\Ngiving a long introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you about\Nyour adopted son Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...adopted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NHe's our child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use playing dumb!\NThe grave of your real child is in Bruntal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You used the fact that\Nthe town office's records had burned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to reapply for a birth certificate\Nas if your child were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come to threaten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a report about Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... A certain man investigated\Nand compiled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This person...\NHe came to sell us insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's former police detective\NRichard Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Former police detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins in 1986,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,when a certain East German government\Nofficial sought refuge in West Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Money?\NHe's not interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why would he\Nstick around a tycoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it when you were a kid,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd take a line of ants...\Nand play around with them...like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe something\Nso terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you\Ndon't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your son\Nwhen he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you couldn't\Nhave children afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy about\Nyour son's age appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, he had money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave you a wonderful house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave you a beautiful yard.\NAnd he gave you affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why\Nyou want to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's written there is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been his parents\Nfor nearly five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of him, my friend,\NRichard, is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now,\Na man called Tenma is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to do something\Nthat cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Besides that...you'll become like\Nthe middle-aged couples mentioned here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Johan's foster parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The apple tree has borne small fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Next year,\Nthey'll be even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be killed by\Na Japanese man soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Johan told those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this, he doesn't have\Nany wish to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NIt's difficult to think like a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a nuclear war burned everything\Nto the ground, he'd still survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All we've done was for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't even save Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't locate Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even stop him from killing Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein,\Nlet's calm down and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with a line of ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even ants...have souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, we've got to\Ntake desperate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk directly\Nto that tycoon Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Fifty more seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll be packed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For Mr. Schuwald's\Nbook donation ceremony tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Lots of big names\Nwill be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Schuwald does something,\Nit's big news, even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The library will soon be closing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The library will soon be closing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,\Ncould you get that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That Czech dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed a Czech picture book,\Nbut I didn't know what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend suddenly collapsed\Nwhen he read this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that maybe the contents of\Nthis book had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your friend get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Completely.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time,\Nin a land far away..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"There lived a nameless monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster was\Ndying to have a name."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"So the monster set out\Non a journey."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What an odd book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closed tomorrow\Nfor the ceremony.
